data.description: Welcome to 2030 Season Ridge Blvd, where this custom-built cottage by Jagoe Homes awaits. Step inside and discover a delightful surprise - the great room, featuring a cathedral ceiling and beautiful laminate floors, exudes a sense of spaciousness and style. This open and airy layout is designed for modern living, with a pass-through to the kitchen seamlessly connecting the great room to the heart of the home. The kitchen is both functional and inviting, equipped with essential appliances including the range/oven, microwave, and dishwasher. It opens up to a dining area, making mealtimes and gatherings a breeze.  A patio door leads you from the dining area to the backyard, creating a smooth transition between indoor and outdoor living. The backyard is both practical and inviting, showcasing a good-sized yard with a concrete patio, perfect for hosting summertime BBQs and entertaining family and friends. You'll also find a 12x12 storage shed, adding to the convenience and utility of the outdoor space. Beyond the beauty of the great room and the convenience of the kitchen, this property offers even more with its oversized attached 1.5-car that's almost as spacious as a typical 2-car garage. Measuring an impressive 375 square feet, the garage provides ample room for hobbies and additional storage.
